Liu Zhen did everything to write this.

149
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:26,600
It is something that is seen
as a treasure by all of you.

150
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:27,799
No.

151
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:33,399
What?

152
00:11:33,590 --> 00:11:34,840
Are you reluctant to give it up?

153
00:11:37,159 --> 00:11:38,039
Sure.

154
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:39,919
If you want to protect it,

155
00:11:42,279 --> 00:11:44,320
get rid of your noble behavior

156
00:11:44,519 --> 00:11:46,039
and kneel before me.

157
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:49,000
Bow to me from now on,

158
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:52,320
be my trapped servant.

159
